## When `XRDisplaySubsystem.running` stays false (checklist)

Work **one change at a time**: XR Plug-in Management (Android OpenXR only, no conflicting legacy provider) → OpenXR Android **Meta Quest Support** + **Oculus Touch** → Player Vulkan / API level → single **AudioListener** → verify **`Assets/Editor/BoreDoomXrManagementBootstrap`** ran (open Editor once) → rebuild APK. Optional sanity check: temporary **DebugXRScene** with authored **XR Origin** only (no runtime bootstrap) to separate “platform config” from “bootstrap code”. Long Copilot/human discussion lives in **`CopilotRef`**.

